Arthur Tauchert https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Arthur_Tauchert 0 Arthur Michael Tauchert (pronounced "Torcher") (21 August 1877 – 27 November 1933) was an Australian acrobatic comedian, dancer, singer, film actor, and star of the Australian silent movie, The Sentimental Bloke (1919). Arthur_Michael_Tauchert ( pronounced " Torcher " ) ( 21 August_1877 – 27_November_1933 ) was an_Australian_acrobatic_comedian , dancer , singer , film_actor , and star of the_Australian_silent_movie , The_Sentimental_Bloke ( 1919 ) .
